<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>Roadster Revival | Pinterest</title>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* Basic Reset */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
        }

        /* Full Screen Background */
        .background {
            background: url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x1000?text=Elegant+Roadster+Revival') no-repeat center center/cover;
            height: 100vh;
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            background-attachment: fixed;
        }

        /* Overlay on Background for Contrast */
        .background-overlay {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); /* Transparent black for darkening the background */
        }

        /* Contact Box Styling */
        .contact-box {
            position: relative;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h3 {
            font-size: 28px;
            color: #E60023; /* Pinterest Red */
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .contact-info {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .contact-info a {
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #E60023; /* Pinterest Red */
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-top: 10px;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .contact-info a:hover {
            color: #B22222; /* Darker Pinterest Red on hover */
        }

        .contact-info i {
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        /* Button Style */
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #E60023; /* Pinterest Red */
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            font-size: 16px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-top: 20px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #B22222; /* Darker Pinterest Red on hover */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Full Screen Background Section -->
    <div class="background">
        <div class="background-overlay"></div>
        <div class="contact-box">
            <h3>Contact Info - Roadster Revival</h3>
            <p class="contact-info">Roadster Revival is your go-to destination for everything related to classic cars and roadsters. We restore and transform vintage roadsters into high-performance machines, while preserving their timeless beauty. Join us on Pinterest for more amazing car designs and restoration projects!</p>
            <p class="contact-info">Stay inspired with our collection of classic roadsters and automotive restoration ideas on our Pinterest page. Explore unique car designs, tips, and projects that showcase the true beauty of classic automobiles.</p>
            <a href="https://www.pinterest.com/roadsterrevival" target="_blank" class="btn">
                <i class="fab fa-pinterest"></i> Follow Us on Pinterest
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
